            <title>[LU-1837] 2.1.3&lt;-&gt;2.3 Test failure on test suite mmp, subtest test_8</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1837</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/98d8d016-f6d7-11e1-b320-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/98d8d016-f6d7-11e1-b320-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_8 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;test_8 failed with 1&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== mmp test 8: mount during e2fsck == 03:14:08 (1346753648)
Force e2fsck checking on device /dev/lvm-MDS/P1 on mds1
CMD: client-29vm7 debugfs -w -R &apos;ssv free_blocks_count 0&apos; /dev/lvm-MDS/P1
client-29vm7: debugfs 1.42.3.wc3 (15-Aug-2012)
CMD: client-29vm7 /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/e2fsck.exp /dev/lvm-MDS/P1
